hopobject.body: I'm in a band pygeum where to buy "Hummingbird pays more attention to each word in the query, ensuring the whole query is taken into account — so if a resulting page is a bit less strong in general, but it's the most relevant to your search terms, that's the result you'll get," a Google spokesman said in an emailed statement. "And if there are plenty of relevant matches to your search terms, Hummingbird does a better job picking the strongest page for you."
